T1  - Comparing with the average: Reference points and market reactions to above-average earnings surprises
AU  - He, Wen
AU  - Li, Yan
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 117
SP  - 105824
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/08/01/
SN  - 0378-4266
